long_description: it is with these words in our hearts that we sought to create the most realistic real life custom saber experience with focus on bringing together superior craftsmanship and engineering with the latest saber props technology. at sabertrio, we build premium duel-ready custom sabers that are inspired by a certain elegant weapon from a galaxy far, far away. founded in 2016 by three individuals, sabertrio was born out of a passion for a certain galaxy far, far away....and above that, to bring custom sabers to life. starting from a small desk, we embarked on our quest to craft fully functioning duel-ready custom sabers that most importantly, were well made and original in design. today, sabertrio is a company that embodies the premium custom saber experience. we strive to deliver on this promise through open communication, transparency and honesty. we do all these because ultimately, we want you to have a truly memorable custom saber experience with us. best builders on the market. there isn't a better saber company in the galaxy.

generated_description: sabertrio, legally known as sabertrio sdn. bhd., is a company based in kuala lumpur, malaysia, specializing in the design and manufacture of premium duel-ready custom sabers. founded in 2016, sabertrio is recognized for its meticulously assembled and hand-finished products, inspired by a galaxy far, far away. the company offers a wide range of custom sabers, including ready-to-ship options and bespoke designs, known for their durability, blade illumination, and advanced electronics. sabertrio is committed to providing high-quality craftsmanship and exceptional customer service, ensuring a memorable experience for its clients.
